builds.name: Slim
builds.description: A lean, slender frame. Quick and light on your feet.

builds.name: Average
builds.description: A balanced, unremarkable physique. Nothing stands out.

builds.name: Athletic
builds.description: A fit, well-toned body. The mark of an active lifestyle.

builds.name: Muscular
builds.description: A powerful, heavily-built frame. Strength is your advantage.

builds.name: Heavy
builds.description: A large, substantial build. Hard to move, harder to stop.

skinTones.name: Pale
skinTones.description: Porcelain skin, rarely touched by sun.

skinTones.name: Fair
skinTones.description: Light skin with a healthy warmth.

skinTones.name: Dark
skinTones.description: Deep, dark skin with a natural sheen.

hairColors.name: Brown
hairColors.description: Common brown hair in various shades.

hairColors.name: Black
hairColors.description: Jet black hair, dark as night.

hairColors.name: Gray
hairColors.description: Silver or gray hair, whether from age or nature.

hairColors.name: White
hairColors.description: Pure white hair, striking and unusual.

hairColors.name: Bald
hairColors.description: No hair at all, by choice or circumstance.
